&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1jcl3cw&quot; data-start=&quot;1649&quot; data-end=&quot;1822&quot;&gt;Design and ship features end-to-end across the stack—Angular front-end through PHP/Symfony and Go back-end services, against MySQL—taking ownership from spec to production&lt;/li&gt;
