&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;w17lzn&quot; data-start=&quot;2005&quot; data-end=&quot;2127&quot;&gt;Operate independently on ambiguous problems, breaking down scope, surfacing risks early, and shipping in safe increments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1kofi9k&quot; data-start=&quot;2128&quot; data-end=&quot;2262&quot;&gt;Partner cross-functionally with product, design, data engineering, infrastructure, and content on features that span team boundaries&lt;/li&gt;
